title: Hmmmm..
review: I'm still trying to figure out if I liked the film or not. Far fetched? Yeah... Empowering? Sure... Go in a hole and hide? wait for a savior? Or go forward? No matter WHAT? Hmm...

title: Fantastic acting...
review: This is a character study and although you'll need to watch it ~3 times to 'get it', it's better than an exorcist type film and just as scary because it's taking place in any city in the world
